POD-Credentials

 POD credentials OO wrapper ( see also, author, license, copyright ) 
 instance of this class is capable of setting up POD credentials, as 
  C<see also, author, license, copyright> and returning  it  as string
  Most common use is for automated code generation when credentials footer
  is needed. 

VERSION

0.02

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc POD::Credentials

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=POD-Credentials

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/POD-Credentials

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/POD-Credentials

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/POD-Credentials


